  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Her Voice, Her Rights - Promoting the advancement of women&#x2019;s and girls&#x2019; rights in Afghanistan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BBC Media Action&#x2019;s three-year project Her Voice, Her Rights  supports civil society organisations (CSOs) to empower women and girls in Afghanistan by enabling them to play an increased role in public discourse. This will involve strengthening the capacity of Afghanistan-based local civil society &#x2013; including non-profit media and women&apos;s rights-focused CSOs &#x2013; to enable them to establish and strengthen networks, coordinate effectively with each other and increase the representation and participation of women and girls in decision-making at household, local and national level.</narrative>
  </description>
